{{Short description|獵戶座的行星狀星雲}}
{{Infobox nebula
 | name      = NGC 2022
 | image     = [[image:The_Inky_Abyss.tif|250px]]
 | caption   = [[哈伯太空望遠鏡|哈伯太空望遠鏡]]拍攝的NGC 2022。<ref name=st/>
